+    // The footer date is now human-friendly + culture-invariant, e.g. "on July 10, 2026 at 5:14 PM".
+    // Story 10.4: the footer clock is now "on {PortalDates day} at HH:mm UTC±HH:mm" (24-hour + machine-local zone
